name: Vochoneta I - Vocho Lindo y Querido #3
description:
To celebrate blessings in disguise. 

Where there are limitations, creativity thrives. It seems counterintuitive, but creative thinking benefits from constraints far more than from freedom.

Vochoneta is a name given in Mexico to the union of a Vocho (Volkswagen Beetle) and a van, truck, or wagon ("camioneta").
